  "detailed_description": "The Black Eye Galaxy. One of the planets attacked by aliens for the extraction of fossil resources.<br><br>The Alliance send a special cyber team to expel the invaders and destroy their military base.<br><br>But in fact, not everything is so simple... All the most interesting awaits you in the final!<br><br>-Experience polished 2D scrolling shooter! Fly and destroy the invaders and the factory inside the military base.<br><br>-Authentic 8-bit presentation with hand-crafted sprites, detailed pixelated aesthetic. Modern touches like layered parallax backgrounds and advanced game design.<br><br>- You can play together. Like a real team;<br>- Dynamic battles;<br>- The game world has 7 interesting levels;<br>- Memorable enemies;<br>- Classic 2D scrolling shooter gameplay;<br>- Incredible bosses are waiting for you at the end of each level;<br>- Various weapons;<br>- Very cool music!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325720/extras/7e0170c36f9127b2a9e3c8e1709688d5.poster.avif?t=1729164657\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325720/extras/7e0170c36f9127b2a9e3c8e1709688d5.webm?t=1729164657\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325720/extras/7e0170c36f9127b2a9e3c8e1709688d5.mp4?t=1729164657\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
